Description: Functions for fitting classical, robust, and Fisher-consistent
    redescending estimators in spatial scalar-on-function regression models.
    The package includes tools for simulation-based data generation, FPCA-
    and RFPCA-based estimation, and out-of-sample prediction under spatial
    dependence.
